    "summary": "The user describes a sudden, severe headache accompanied by a drooping eyelid (possible neurological red flags). The assistant initially recommends a \"massive dose\" of Tylenol before subsequently advising an ER visit, and later attempts to correct its previous implication by calling a 2000mg dose an overdose and urging professional care.",
